Dependencies:
wget
xdeb
gawk
sed
w3m

Installation:
git clone https://github.com/poach3r/sift/
chmod +x ~/sift/sift.sh
sudo mv ~/sift/sift.sh /usr/bin

Usage:
sudo sift.sh [PACKAGE]

To change mirror location, modify line 4.

Roadmap:
1. Create an actual command
2. Easy Mirror Changing
3. Non-Free repo access
4. Decrease dependencies & switch to curl
5. Auto completing package names (ie no more copy pasting the real package name)
